replies.author: mine新时代xs
replies.txt_content:
[11:30:25] [Server thread/WARN]: Can't keep up! Did the system time change, or is the server overloaded? Running 5512ms behind, skipping 110 tick(s)
你的服务器严重超载，1tick本来需要0.05秒，但现在1tick超过1分钟，可以理解为主线程卡死
绝对是土豆服，联系你的服务商咨询开你这个服务器所需求的配置以解决

replies.author: xmdhs
replies.txt_content: 土豆服务器吗，在 Server.properties 中设置 max-tick-time=60000 为 max-tick-time=-1
